Demonstration of Proposed Features:

The Heart Disease Analysis Dashboard developed using Tableau demonstrates the following key features:

>>>  Interactive Heart Disease Overview:

        Displays total heart disease cases and overall distribution.
        Provides comparative insights across age groups, gender, and race.
        Dynamic filters for Age, Gender, and Race enable customized analysis.

>>>  Demographic Analysis:

        Compares heart disease prevalence across different age categories and gender groups.
        Identifies high-risk demographic segments.

>>> Lifestyle Impact Analysis:

        Visualizes the impact of smoking, alcohol consumption, and physical activity on heart disease.
        Helps understand how lifestyle behaviors influence cardiovascular health.

>>> Health Status & Risk Group Identification

        Examines general health condition versus heart disease occurrence.
        Highlights patients suffering from multiple conditions such as stroke, diabetes, and heart disease.

>>> User-Friendly Interactive Filters

        Allows users to apply filters dynamically.
        Provides real-time updates for better comparative analysis.
        Ensures smooth navigation and easy interpretation of complex medical data.
